        "body": "- Supabase for cloud database\r\n- Added Supabase client config (src/lib/supabase.js)\r\n- Added API service with fetchInquiries, postInquiry, updateInquiryStatus (src/services/api.js)\r\n- Contact form now submits inquiries to Supabase\r\n- Created premium dark admin dashboard with:\r\n  - Stat cards (Total, Not Started, In Process, Done)\r\n  - Search bar with clear button\r\n  - Status filter pills with counts\r\n  - Inquiry cards with status management (Not Started / In Process / Done)\r\n  - Action toolbar (Refresh, Export CSV, Activity Log, Settings)\r\n  - Animated loading spinner\r\n  - Admin footer with links\r\n- Added admin authentication:\r\n  - AuthContext with localStorage session persistence\r\n  - ProtectedRoute component for route guarding\r\n  - Login page with password gate\r\n  - DASHBOARD link visible in navbar only when authenticated\r\n  - Logout button on Dashboard page\r\n- Updated App.jsx with AuthProvider, Login, and protected Dashboard routes\r\n- Updated Header.jsx with conditional Dashboard nav link\r\n- Updated Layout.jsx with Dashboard title mapping",
